# Deny-all build context. Only one file is referenced from any Dockerfile
# (IsaacDockerfile: COPY CL_isaaclab_sim/requirements.txt). Everything else
# is bind-mounted at runtime via docker-compose.yml, so sending it to the
# daemon is wasted bandwidth (~11 GB on full builds otherwise).
*
!CL_isaaclab_sim
CL_isaaclab_sim/*
!CL_isaaclab_sim/requirements.txt
